Lectura de la base de datos

zonaA <- read.table("ZoneA.dat", na.strings = "-999.9999", header = TRUE)

Exploratorio inicial

library(geoR)

Variograma emp√≠rico

library(geoR)
v3 <- variog(gzonaA, max.dist = 15000, uvec = c(0, seq(2000, 15000, 500)))
## variog: computing omnidirectional variogram
plot(v3)

Evidencia de estructura espacial

envMC <- variog.mc.env(gzonaA, obj.variog = v3, nsim = 1000)
## variog.env: generating 1000 simulations by permutating data values
## variog.env: computing the empirical variogram for the 1000 simulations
## variog.env: computing the envelops
plot(v3, envelope.obj = envMC)

Estimaci√≥n de par√°metros

M√°xima verosimilitud

library(geoR)
modelo2_lik <- likfit(gzonaA, ini.cov.pars = c(0.8, 4000/3),
                      fix.nugget = TRUE,
                      cov.model = "exp")

Graficaci√≥n de modelos

plot(v3, pch = 19)
lines(modelo2_lik, lty = 1, col = "black")
legend("bottomright", legend = c("MaxLik"), 
       col = c("black"), 
       lty = c(1))

Verificaci√≥n de modelos

envModLik <- variog.model.env(gzonaA, obj.variog = v3,
                              model.pars = modelo2_lik, 
                              nsim = 1000)
## Warning in if (class(model.pars) == "eyefit") {: la condici√≥n tiene
## longitud > 1 y s√≥lo el primer elemento ser√° usado
## variog.env: generating 1000 simulations (with  85 points each) using the function grf
## variog.env: adding the mean or trend
## variog.env: computing the empirical variogram for the 1000 simulations
## variog.env: computing the envelops
plot(v3, envelope.obj = envModLik)

Predicci√≥n del modelo

puntos_pred <- pred_grid(c(0, 20000), c(0, 16000), by = 100)

KC <- krige.control(type = "sk", obj.mod = modelo2_lik)
sk <- krige.conv(gzonaA, krige = KC, loc = puntos_pred)
## krige.conv: model with constant mean
## krige.conv: Kriging performed using global neighbourhood
pred.lim <- range(c(sk$pred))
sd.lim <- range(sqrt(c(sk$kr)))

image(sk, col = gray(seq(1, 0, l = 101)), zlim = pred.lim)
contour(sk, add = T, levels = seq(12,17, 0.5))
points(gzonaA, add = TRUE, cex.max = 2)

image(sk, value = sqrt(sk$krige.var), col = gray(seq(1, 0.3, l = 51)), zlim = sd.lim)
contour(sk, value = sqrt(sk$krige.var), levels = seq(0, 1, by = 0.1), add = T)
points(gzonaA$coords, pch = "+")
